        "name": "Crushing Fist (Physical)",
        "description": "<div><p>The Armor Construct swings one of its massive fists at a target with incredible force, dealing D6 Bludgeoning damage.</p></div>"
      },
      {
        "startDie": 3,
        "endDie": 4,
        "name": "Arcane Shield",
        "description": "<div><p>The Armor Construct raises its arms, summoning a shimmering arcane shield that provides it with a boost to Health equal to half its maximum Health. This additional Health can go over the Armor Construct's usual max, but lasts until the start of the its next turn.</p></div>"
      },
      {
        "startDie": 5,
        "endDie": 6,
        "name": "Rune Strike (Physical)",
        "description": "<div><p>The Armor Construct channels its power into a devastating melee attack. It makes a melee attack against a target, dealing D8 Slashing damage. If the attack hits, the target must succeed on an Endurance check or be Paralyzed for 1 round.</p></div>"
      }
    ],
    "description": "<div><p>The Vaelorian often bound spirits to suits of armor to achieve the perfect sentinel, patrolling and seeking out those who dare trespass upon its creator's domain. Armor Constructs are always an imposing sight, composed of heavy metal plates interlocked to form the appearance of an armored humanoid figure. Its surface is adorned with intricate runes and sigils, pulsing with an ominous glow. With every step, the ground trembles beneath its weight, and its mighty gauntleted fists can pulverize solid stone with ease.</p></div>",
